heading: Corporations, Foreign. Law and legislation. United States. States.
general-note: Here are entered collective works on state laws governing corporations organized under the laws of one state and operating in other states. Works on the law of an individual state governing the operations within the state of corporations organized under the laws of another state are entered under. Corporations, Foreign--Law and legislation,. further subdivided by the name of the individual state. Works on federal laws governing foreign corporations operating in the United States are entered under. Corporations, Foreign--Law and legislation--United States..
